notes:
Pre-Launcher pops up (which normally starts the anti-hack protection) and the game hangs with the following message in the log.
5411.432:0083:0084:trace:seh:call_stack_handlers calling handler at 0x7bc805f0 code=c0000005 flags=10
5411.432:0083:0084:trace:seh:call_stack_handlers handler at 0x7bc805f0 returned 2
Until it eventually overflows. Game must be killed via task manager at this point.
